---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How we collect, use, and protect personal information on AVL Curious."
  noindex={true}
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16 sm:py-20 prose">
    <h1 class="font-display text-mountain-900">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-mountain-500"><em>Draft — last updated 2026-05-05.</em>
      <strong>This is a placeholder pending broker-in-charge review and counsel sign-off.</strong>
    </p>

    <h2>What we collect</h2>
    <p>When you submit a contact or lead form on this site, we collect your name, email address, phone number, and the answers you provide (budget, timeline, interest, message). We also collect basic analytics data — pages visited, referring URL, approximate location, and device — via Google Analytics 4, only after you accept cookies.</p>

    <h2>How we use it</h2>
    <p>Lead-form data is emailed to Karin Wulff for personal follow-up. Analytics data is used in aggregate to understand which pages and topics readers find useful so we can improve the site. We do not sell or rent your data.</p>

    <h2>Third-party processors</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Form submissions are processed by our form-handling provider (Web3Forms or Formspree).</li>
      <li>Analytics by Google Analytics 4.</li>
      <li>Hosting on Amazon Web Services (S3 + CloudFront).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use Google Analytics cookies once you accept the cookie banner. No advertising cookies are used.</p>

    <h2>Your choices</h2>
    <p>To request your data, request deletion, or ask any privacy question, email <a href="mailto:karin@fuzzywolfsales.com">karin@fuzzywolfsales.com</a>.</p>

    <h2>Real estate disclosures</h2>
    <p>Listings displayed under IDX are subject to Canopy MLS terms and used for the personal, non-commercial use of consumers identifying prospective properties.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
